PrecisEnactment of the PRESCRIBED DEPOSITS (BANKS WITHOUT DEPOSIT INSURANCE) REGULATIONS which itemize the exceptions to the minimum deposit requirement of $150,000 imposed on full-service foreign banks operating in Canada whose deposits are not insured by the Canada Deposit Insurance Corporation.
